name: The Point Is Conceded
Lore: 'Political pressure carefully applied with a generous helping of Republic procedure can negate the strongest of motions.',
Text: 'If you have a senate majority, activate 1 Force. OR If your opponent has a senate majority, place your senator at Galactic Senate in Used Pile to place an opponent''s character present (your choice) in opponent''s Used Pile. (Immune to Sense.)',
